Open the editor by:

* Clicking ''New…'' next to the Console's profile dropdown (creates an empty profile and opens it).
* Clicking ''Edit'' next to the profile dropdown when a profile is selected.
* Clicking the ''Edit in form'' button atop any profile tiddler's view (provided by the plugin's ViewTemplate).

